    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Ofqual welcomes DfE announcement on 2021 exams
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Ofqual will continue to work closely with exam boards, unions and other stakeholders on contingencies for all possible scenarios.</p>

  </div>
</div>

